  "title": "Architectural Supervisor (Construction)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Review, coordinate, and produce architectural shop drawings and related works for projects.</li>\n  <li>Supervise and inspect architectural works carried out by subcontractors on site.</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with architectural specifications, Singapore Building Codes, and quality standards such as BCA CONQUAS.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate architectural services with other trades and manage scheduling, material requisition, cost control, and documentation.</li>\n  <li>Monitor adherence to project timelines, quality, and safety standards.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Building/Architecture or equivalent</li>\n  <li>At least 5 years’ relevant experience in the <strong>Construction industry.</strong></li>\n  <li>Strong knowledge of Singapore Building Codes, regulations, and local quality standards.</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with construction safety requirements</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in <strong>MS Word</strong> to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
